 {"id":"git_safety_guard-kldl","title":"Command Telemetry: CLI query commands","notes":"
---

## Additional CLI Features

### Pagination Support

Add `--offset` and `--limit` for all list commands:

```
dcg telemetry recent --offset 100 --limit 20   # Skip first 100, show 20
dcg telemetry blocks --offset 50 --limit 10
dcg telemetry search "pattern" --offset 0 --limit 50
```

### SQL Injection Protection

For the raw query command, enforce read-only:

```rust
fn validate_query(sql: &str) -> Result<(), QueryError> {
    let sql_upper = sql.to_uppercase();

    // Block modification statements
    let blocked = ["INSERT", "UPDATE", "DELETE", "DROP", "ALTER", "CREATE", "TRUNCATE"];
    for keyword in blocked {
        if sql_upper.contains(keyword) {
            return Err(QueryError::WriteNotAllowed(keyword.to_string()));
        }
    }

    // Also block ATTACH (could access other databases)
    if sql_upper.contains("ATTACH") {
        return Err(QueryError::AttachNotAllowed);
    }

    Ok(())
}
```

